column2: SELECT    m.ra as my_ra,   m.dec as my_dec,   m.z as my_z,   s.objid,    s.ra,    s.dec,    s.z,   e.lgm_tot_p5# as mass    into mydb.SpecCompanions from MyDB.Sample5#_coord_ID AS m   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, @radius) AS n    LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON n.objID=s.objID   LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON s.specObjID=e.specObjID   WHERE n.objID = s.objID     AND s.z is not null
